<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,800;0,900;1,700&family=DM+Sans:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
body{width:1200px;height:630px;overflow:hidden;background:#0d0b04;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;position:relative}
body::before{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;background:radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 60% at 60% 50%,rgba(212,165,52,0.1) 0%,transparent 70%)}
.left{flex:1;padding:64px 56px;position:relative;z-index:2}
.right{width:420px;padding:48px 40px 48px 0;position:relative;z-index:2;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center}
.eyebrow{font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(212,165,52,0.6);font-weight:700;margin-bottom:16px}
.title{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:42px;font-weight:900;color:#fff;line-height:1.1;margin-bottom:28px}
.title em{color:#d4a534;font-style:normal}
.pain-item{display:flex;gap:14px;align-items:flex-start;margin-bottom:14px}
.pain-x{color:#e74c3c;font-size:16px;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px;font-weight:700}
.pain-text{font-size:15px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);line-height:1.6}
.quote{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:20px;color:#d4a534;font-style:italic;font-weight:700;margin-top:24px;line-height:1.4}
.divider{width:1px;background:rgba(212,165,52,0.15);height:100%;margin:0 0 0 40px;flex-shrink:0}
.brand{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:28px;font-weight:900;color:#fff;margin-bottom:6px}
.brand span{color:#d4a534}
.brand-sub{font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3);letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:32px}
.stat{margin-bottom:20px}
.stat-num{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:32px;font-weight:800;color:#d4a534;line-height:1}
.stat-label{font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3);letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-top:3px}
.cta{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:#25d366;color:#052a10;padding:12px 24px;border-radius:10px;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;margin-top:8px}
.url{font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);margin-top:16px;letter-spacing:0.06em}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="left">
  <div class="eyebrow">Punjabi Finance</div>
  <div class="title">Watch a Real Portfolio.<br><em>Every Move. Every Trade.</em></div>
  <div class="pain-item"><span class="pain-x">✗</span><span class="pain-text">Experts who give opinions but never show their real portfolio</span></div>
  <div class="pain-item"><span class="pain-x">✗</span><span class="pain-text">Content that sounds smart but doesn't help your decisions</span></div>
  <div class="pain-item"><span class="pain-x">✗</span><span class="pain-text">Not knowing how experienced investors actually think in real time</span></div>
  <div class="quote">"So I decided to share everything."</div>
</div>
<div class="divider"></div>
<div class="right">
  <div class="brand">Punjabi <span>Finance</span></div>
  <div class="brand-sub">punjabifinance.com</div>
  <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">200+</div><div class="stat-label">Members Inside</div></div>
  <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">$10</div><div class="stat-label">Per Month</div></div>
  <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">Real Portfolio</div><div class="stat-label">Live Holdings &amp; Trades</div></div>
  <div class="cta">&#128172; Join the Community</div>
  <div class="url">punjabifinance.com/community</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
